      • append

        References append(Iterable<?>... references)
        Combines the references in this with the specified references. The Iterable can contain instances of String or Reference. Note that all instances of References are suitable iterables.

        It is implementation specific whether or not this is modified or whether a new object is returned instead. If this is modified it should also be returned.

        Parameters:
        references - The reference to append
        Returns:
        The combined references object
